node.text:
So I did a thing ⚡️♠️

I may be smiling in this photo but I was huffing and puffing like a fat kid… I can assure you 😆

I’ve been making a conscious effort to step out of my comfort zone. Going to @zrteamnc for the first time by myself put my anxiety through the roof. BUT I am so grateful I did because I LOVE IT!! 

You never know what doors will open for you once you step out into the unknown. 🖤

node.text:
You reap what you sow 🌱🖤

A simple phrase that has stood the test of time because of its powerful meaning… that is, your future is shaped by your actions today. 

In a world that is full of uncertainty and chaos, be deliberate and firm in your actions. Be aware of who and what you are investing your time and energy in… and always be working towards your goals. 

And yes… my shirt still has paint on it. I am aware. 🤓🖤🤘🏼
